{"tid":1469431,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"屌你咩,道咩撚野歉","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:34.000Z","uid":221856,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f43dca88ae82b27d9b763ba825ce82f69cb121f","tid":1469431,"uid":221856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:49:35.000Z","msg":"口裡說不 身體卻很誠實<br />\n話不割蓆, 你道歉咪割緊蓆囉<br />\n<br />\n建制就做到真正不割蓆<br />\n何妖攪咁大單, 有無建制出黎道過歉<br />\n<br />\n而家打仗呀 無人會欣賞你地道德高尚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516a90020b1e37ed8dc53c7f537f27abe23bcc24","tid":1469431,"uid":95487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27e7fe48886b65d8b6aec2c42d183a8c2a47283","tid":1469431,"uid":182774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01